{"tid":386941,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔公平?】超專業分析 網友 : 最受歡迎港姐無可能係張寶欣","createTime":"2017-09-04T09:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T17:40:19.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dbdee21a748a5a5dacd34d13b3db1aaa7c991ad9","tid":386941,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170904/large/1504512608_d76b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170904%2Flarge%2F1504512608_d76b.jpg&h=cf191252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170904/large/1504512610_9174.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170904%2Flarge%2F1504512610_9174.png&h=4f8e2631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年香港小姐競選決賽不斷Hard Sell大台直播App，就連友誼小姐一獎都改做「big big channel最受歡迎香港小姐」。此獎項以直播App上網友給的心心作標準，稱以最高心心數量的佳麗奪得，最後獎項由10號張寶欣獲得。先不論有大量網友投訴直播App在比賽其間完全不能開啟，既然這麼多人未能連線，那心心從哪裡來可說是個迷。賽前被網友極力支持的9號金美黎，不但三甲不入，就連「BBC最受歡迎港姐」都拿不到令他們心心不忿。有網友製作圖表加上超專業的數據分析指出獎項根本不應由10號張寶欣獲得，獲獎的該是9號金美黎，指比賽有不公之嫌。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://is.gd/bBrel3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FbBrel3&d=2O%2FuI0XC9AMasLbiUOLmrP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=51c0d620\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/bBrel3</a><br />\n<br />\n比返個獎人啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962e7e15efd196ac5889aa6135c463014b29ea5d","tid":386941,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:31:03.000Z","msg":"要報icac"},{"pid":"6149d04b38a2b1